{"tid":1562511,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"I have a dream, 連登合唱團入嚟幫幫手","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T04:46:27.000Z","uid":182001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ad46aacf5aa4cfcb16ea6c98feddf85a8c1f16","tid":1562511,"uid":182001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"小弟跪求各位巴打斯打幫幫手，有冇可能喺各大港鐵站或者港鐵商場一齊大合唱呢首二次創作呢？<br />\n<br />\n《黨鐵惡夢》#識唱一齊唱 <br />\n<br />\n原曲：《多啦A夢》主題曲<br />\n改詞：叮三分鐘<br />\n<br />\n全城人士很暴躁　愛黨鐵路真糟糕<br />\n人人圍插   不可思議　<br />\n放棄鐵路   行路更好<br />\n沿途停頓怎樣去　無車封站好恐怖<br />\n橫蠻無理　只識加價　<br />\n公關只懂賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n*迫港鐵沒法趕到　行路又遲到<br />\n（你睇，班車嚟啦！）<br />\n衰撚到　唔好鬼信D廣告　<br />\n各區繼續嘈 (無車繼續嘈)<br />\n<br />\n遲來停頓的預告　<br />\n放工遭遇好恐怖<br />\n人人圍困 噓聲一片　<br />\n放棄鐵路 行路更好<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士一定去　<br />\n晏些少就必趕到<br />\n成棚朋友　不屈不退　<br />\n只得差佬亂警告<br />\n<br />\n*重唱"},{"pid":"e2b5954b2903850941ca2b4984ab29c436dfb6cf","tid":1562511,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}